data.description: WELCOME  TO YOUR HOME in South San Diego!   Don’t miss this opportunity. One floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, Nice front yard with green Turf,  Central A/C, 4 tubular skylights, Kitchen recessed ceiling light, Kitchen cabinets granite countertop, stove/range conveys with the sale, kitchen tile flooring. Big living and family room with  gas and or wood fireplace , wood laminate flooring. Primary Bedroom with private Bathroom , 3 bedrooms with carpet and mirrored closet doors. 1 bedroom tile flooring. Cozy back patio with a gazebo and green turf. Garage with sink and washer and dryer hookups, plenty of storage cabinets. Double pane windows. Near  to the Park, High School, fast food, shopping center and more. The house is sold “As-Is” Seller will not do any repairs.
